#### Start Project 
`npm init`   <br />
`npm init -y`  <br />

#### Install SASS 
`npm install -D node-sass nodemon` <br />

#### Set in the Package.json this two lines 
`"build-css": "node-sass --include-path scss scss/prueba.scss css/pruebacss.css"` <br />
`"watch-css": "nodemons -e scss -x \"npm run build-css\""` <br />
<br />
